text_raw:
3. The area consisting of the Local Electoral Area of Ennis is prescribed as 
a rent pressure zone during the period commencing on 31 August 2023 and 
ending on 31 December 2024. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

30 August, 2023. 

DARRAGH O’BRIEN, 

Minister for Housing, Local Government and Heritage. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 1st September, 2023.

text_raw:
EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

This Order provides for the designation of the Local Electoral Area of Ennis as 
a rent pressure zone under section 24A of the Residential Tenancies Act 2004 
(as inserted by section 36 of the Planning and Development (Housing) and 
Residential Tenancies Act 2016), for the period commencing on 31 August 2023 
and ending on 31 December 2024.
